    <p>Create a maze solver using recursive backtracking algorithm:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>Part 1: Maze Representation and Generation</b><br/>
