        <b>Benefits of Polymorphism:</b>
        <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
            <table style="width: 100%;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;"><b>Flexibility</b></td>
