    <h3>Common Tkinter Errors and Solutions</h3>
    <table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; margin: 15px 0; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <thead>
            <tr style="background-color: #dc3545; color: white;">
                <th>Error</th>
                <th>Cause</th>
                <th>Solution</th>
                <th>Example</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td><b>TclError</b></td>
                <td>Wrong widget name or property</td>
                <td>Check spelling and widget existence</td>
                <td><code>label.packk()</code> → <code>label.pack()</code></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>PhotoImage disappears</b></td>
                <td>Garbage collection removes image</td>
                <td>Store reference as instance variable</td>
                <td><code>self.photo = PhotoImage(file="x.png")</code></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Window too small</b></td>
                <td>Widgets not expanding properly</td>
                <td>Use <code>fill='both', expand=True</code></td>
                <td><code>frame.pack(fill='both', expand=True)</code></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Nothing appears</b></td>
                <td>Forgot <code>mainloop()</code></td>
                <td>Always call <code>root.mainloop()</code></td>
                <td>Last line should be <code>mainloop()</code></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Widgets overlapping</b></td>
                <td>Wrong packing order/side</td>
                <td>Plan layout before coding</td>
                <td>Use frames to organize sections</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Console freezes</b></td>
                <td>Long operation in main thread</td>
                <td>Use <code>after()</code> for long tasks</td>
                <td><code>root.after(100, long_function)</code></td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

