<b>d. Input Validation Techniques</b><br/>

<b>1. Real-time Validation:</b>
<div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
    <pre>
        def validate_email(event=None):
            email = entry_email.get()
            if "@" not in email or "." not in email.split("@")[-1]:
                entry_email.config(bg="#ffcccc")  # Light red
            else:
                entry_email.config(bg="white")

        # Bind validation to key release
        entry_email.bind("<KeyRelease>", validate_email)
    </pre>
</div>

