        User types<br/>
        └── Clicks Search<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;└── SQL LIKE query<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;└── Results displayed
